        "**Treatment Plan:**  A tailored treatment plan should prioritize KRAS G12C inhibitors and immunotherapy, with careful consideration of potential combinations.  Close monitoring for treatment response and toxicity is crucial.",
        "**Comorbidity Management:**  A detailed plan for managing the patient's comorbidities (diabetes, hypertension, osteoarthritis) should be implemented to minimize treatment-related complications.",
        "**Clinical Trial Consideration:**  The patient should be assessed for eligibility in relevant clinical trials.",
